{"tid":511112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過度沉迷玩家視為精神問題患者 ﻿打機成癮﻿﻿將納國際疾病﻿","createTime":"2017-12-27T06:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T04:51:59.000Z","uid":13468,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd41194bce7f1efc30551e246b883c1a9d43092","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"過度沉迷玩家視為精神問題患者 ﻿打機成癮﻿﻿將納國際疾病﻿<br />\n<br />\n打機會令人上癮，甚至是一種病。世界衞生組織（WHO）計劃將「打機成癮（Gaming disorder）」納入明年發表的診斷手冊《國際疾病分類》（ICD）中，即打機成癮將正式成為危害心理健康的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n　　世衞在監察電腦遊戲玩家行為長達十年後，決定將部份過度沉迷遊戲的玩家視為精神問題患者。據世衞第十一版ICD草案的描述，「打機成癮」是指持續或反覆的電玩行為模式，包括線上或離線遊戲。草案指，「打機成癮」有三大特徵，包括對次數、頻率、強度、持續時間、結束時間等的控制能力受損；對於遊戲優先的程度大於其他興趣或日常活動；及即使發生負面後果，仍然持續打機。若病人持續有關行為一年或以上，便有機會患上「打機成癮」。<br />\n<br />\n　　世衞心理健康及藥物濫用部門成員波茲尼亞克（Vladimir Poznyak）認為，醫學專家需意識到，打機成癮亦可對健康造成嚴重後果，而患者只屬少數，並舉例指正如喜歡飲酒的人不一定會酒精成癮，但過度沉迷則會導致不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n　　本港家庭醫生鄭志文指，「打機成癮」可被視作一種精神情緒疾病，加上現時已有打機成癮的治療方法，相信納入ICD是好事，因可有助醫學界進行相關研究，對病人而言亦更容易辦理保險索償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/632712/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F632712%2F&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fa98ec37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F632712%2F&h=0321d425\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/632712/</a>"},{"pid":"68d57ff37e0e9438bf07aeceb246c6fdd7c72101","tid":511112,"uid":75638,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"咁係斯咪可以拎白卡咬老綜"},{"pid":"c0bbada9f702b6b8e411385a9e575936ae272989","tid":511112,"uid":108386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係斯咪可以拎白卡咬老綜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60c9f35bde66b41f7e52c51f73af6b75fcd0146","tid":511112,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係斯咪可以拎白卡咬老綜</blockquote><br />\n拎白卡咬老綜繼續打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7331dd6012ae987e214fae4739cd1977b05360ea","tid":511112,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"打j好過打機"},{"pid":"2564a2a297cdf57e69f31cabcc50f4c37f4d9a61","tid":511112,"uid":13258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"<del>返工成癮</del>OT呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386cdf16dbb7b5b0cac6f794a038ed05ef96c106","tid":511112,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"你叫班電競師點算"},{"pid":"04e9611bb550ee599d7d795fd012396192522f62","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"好似支那醫院咁用 anticholinergic agent 對付班毒撚<br />\n<br />\n不停打scopolamine針  搞到班毒撚記憶喪失<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://allnewspipeline.com/images/57FEAScopolamine1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallnewspipeline.com%2Fimages%2F57FEAScopolamine1.jpg&h=38b765de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞最近有不法分子使用一種俗稱為「魔鬼的呼吸」迷藥犯案，以東莨菪鹼（scopolamine）操控受害人意志，使到對方變成行屍走肉，任由擺布，而受害人清醒後根本不記得發生過甚麼事情。<br />\n<br />\n東莨菪鹼源自南美一種開白黃花朵的borrachero樹，此字意指「令你醉倒」，這種樹在哥倫比亞尤其常見。受害人被人用藥後，幾分鐘內便猶如喪屍，失去自由意志，任由歹徒擺布，包括被強姦、提光銀行戶口的錢、協助歹徒在自己的房子搜掠一空等，甚至捐出器官，東莨菪鹼因此又俗稱為「魔鬼的呼吸」。<br />\n<br />\n現時哥倫比亞的毒販正販售這種迷藥，活躍於首都波哥大的毒販布萊克說，這種迷藥只需在街頭向受害人臉上一吹，數分鐘內受害人便會受到控制，而這種迷藥無色無味，故此防不勝防。<br />\n<br />\n女受害者被迷失財<br />\n<br />\n布萊克說：「受害人中招後，你可以把他們當小孩般擺布。」他指出，一克的東莨菪鹼相當於一克的可卡因，它甚至毒過炭疽。在高劑量使用時，東莨菪鹼足以致命。<br />\n<br />\n由於它可以抑制受害人的記憶，受害人清醒後根本不記得發生過甚麼事情。<br />\n<br />\n歹徒也可將東莨菪鹼混入飲品內，讓受害人喝下，令其「中招」。一名女受害人說，一名男子在街上向她問路，她帶路後和對方喝了果汁，之後帶對方返家，把家中一切包括男友的相機和存款悉數交給對方。<br />\n<br />\n英國《臨牀藥物學期刊》指出，東莨菪鹼會令到受害人失去記憶，效果有如使用了diazepam抗焦慮藥。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據報美國中情局在冷戰時期，亦會使用東莨菪鹼向犯人逼供。"},{"pid":"9aab58d6a427b2aca357e75e8256ece79467130c","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"私家精神科醫生又賺一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6f4fc74857c49b93707bbe0a2802c9cad8c9c9","tid":511112,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a44e079d8de659895c6d5db41bd5605a5f52676","tid":511112,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"請病假有無得照出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a8c2c416ef360d8a99291e3224c3c1d1611ad9","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386cdf16dbb7b5b0cac6f794a038ed05ef96c106","tid":511112,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"你叫班電競師點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"收得皮<br />\n<br />\n會俾人歧視"},{"pid":"6c2130edef20394028aa6d423a27505c2d7143fd","tid":511112,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbe562f051967faff57ab6915680390ccef156e","tid":511112,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"騰訊game業務點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:430買左"},{"pid":"75ae0cde24c90be336f098c0efa9265e7aafd097","tid":511112,"uid":42767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0a8c2c416ef360d8a99291e3224c3c1d1611ad9","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386cdf16dbb7b5b0cac6f794a038ed05ef96c106","tid":511112,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"你叫班電競師點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"收得皮<br />\n<br />\n會俾人歧視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"殘奧新項目<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3531765df35db75eb2d8b2c3e2b6534eb3a678ad","tid":511112,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6f4fc74857c49b93707bbe0a2802c9cad8c9c9","tid":511112,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛Epiphany</span>"},{"pid":"48dc55024f7d7cbaa3eb115c1f42bca22c8eea2b","tid":511112,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3531765df35db75eb2d8b2c3e2b6534eb3a678ad","tid":511112,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6f4fc74857c49b93707bbe0a2802c9cad8c9c9","tid":511112,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛Epiphany</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/162811_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F162811_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bfc697fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"990b0ec3fde6449892d6b8e8ce4460f22c08f243","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"藥物治療&ldquo;網癮&rdquo;，原理和我的戒毒是一樣的。人體內有一個&ldquo;獎賞系統&rdquo;，這個系統的物質基礎主要是多巴胺，它的增加、減少調控著人的情緒，興奮或低落。成癮，就是多巴胺的自我調控失衡。毒品，通過外源性的物質使多巴胺含量驟然增加，使人有快感，而網絡、賭博等行為依賴者則是通過內源性物質獲得多巴胺增加，得到快感。我研究東莨菪鹼44年，莨菪，也就是曼陀羅，對多巴胺起伏有很好的平衡作用，也就有&ldquo;除癮&rdquo;功效。<br />\n<br />\n　　記者：聽說您要將這種治療方法推向市場，可迄今為止，您只有13個臨床病例，即便100%成功，能證明這種療法就成熟了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n　　楊國棟：我研究莨菪44年，治療毒癮一萬多例，個個成功。治療網癮和毒癮是一樣的，不過把用藥量降低一半，很安全，保證來一個好一個。我們的辦法是&ldquo;先破後立&rdquo;。 &ldquo;破&rdquo;，就是先打針，一定劑量的東莨菪鹼，抑制大腦皮層，讓人忘了電腦。小孩剛送到戒毒中心時，拳打腳踢，還要割腕自殺，屁股上打一針，就安靜了。所謂&ldquo;立&rdquo;，就是心理干預，採用中醫耳針、中藥調理、外出參觀旅遊等手段，使患者接觸現實生活，培養網絡外的多種興趣。<br />\n<br />\ndevil's breath<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://had.name/data/article/0032-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhad.name%2Fdata%2Farticle%2F0032-1.png&h=3447d9ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e373d44332235baeda6ddb6d2c520256dbffa2d0","tid":511112,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c22cdd69891f80eb22f089d2149735d851319338","tid":511112,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"聽日即刻入紙拎白卡，打足一年機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe1947b4bab6c5d4477315e9f215d2eaa3b3eaf","tid":511112,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}